{"tid":1768931,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"點解無手足講呢單","createTime":"2019-12-04T12:31:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-04T15:03:58.000Z","uid":306664,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b34ec27c2fca8d977780fdb7f098b4991317a139","tid":1768931,"uid":306664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T12:31:21.000Z","msg":"警方上月17日圍堵理工大學期間，有人駕駛私家車企圖撞向警方防線，警方發射實彈還擊，司機其後逃去。警方調查近半個月，終於前日（2日）在旺角拘捕一名裝修工人，控告他襲警、危險駕駛及無牌駕駛等8罪。裝修工今（4日）被押往九龍城裁判法院應訊，暫毋須答辯，不准保釋，還押至明年1月15日再訊。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n救人啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20191204/s00001/1575458065326/%e6%b6%89%e7%84%a1%e7%89%8c%e9%a7%95%e9%a7%9b%e6%92%9e%e8%ad%a6%e9%98%b2%e7%b7%9a-28%e6%ad%b2%e8%a3%9d%e4%bf%ae%e5%b7%a5%e6%b6%89%e8%a5%b2%e8%ad%a6%e5%8d%b1%e9%a7%95%e7%ad%898%e7%bd%aa\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20191204%2Fs00001%2F1575458065326%2F%25e6%25b6%2589%25e7%2584%25a1%25e7%2589%258c%25e9%25a7%2595%25e9%25a7%259b%25e6%2592%259e%25e8%25ad%25a6%25e9%2598%25b2%25e7%25b7%259a-28%25e6%25ad%25b2%25e8%25a3%259d%25e4%25bf%25ae%25e5%25b7%25a5%25e6%25b6%2589%25e8%25a5%25b2%25e8%25ad%25a6%25e5%258d%25b1%25e9%25a7%2595%25e7%25ad%25898%25e7%25bd%25aa&d=sHvBfS5bCv0nfD6zjI7mDZnDkpC49KclrNwegNic%2Fqo%3D&h=cee2f93f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20191204%2Fs00001%2F15